'''''Polyhedron'' 97''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[July]] of [[1994]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Adversaries: Characters for the Star Wars: New Republic Campaign]]" and was written by [[Bill Slavicsek]] and [[Michele Carter]].

